platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Give a location (living room, kitchen, office) and how much light the area gets and this app will recommend the plants most likely to survive there, so you can turn your home into a horticultural haven.

Indiquez un emplacement (salon, cuisine, bureau) et la luminosité dont bénéficient ces zones pour que l’app vous recommande les plantes les plus susceptibles de survivre dans chacune de ces pièces et que vous puissiez transformer votre foyer en un paradis végétal.

Your houseplants will love this app. Simply tell Planta a location (living room, kitchen, office) and how much light the area gets and the app will recommend the plants most likely to survive there. Maybe a pothos for shady spots, a moth orchid for sunnier ones. With Planta, you can turn your home into a horticultural haven.
